\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh well, just a black mark, that's all.
