ying for myself, I weren't a bad scholar when I was going school. I learned all I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Your parents were interested in what you did?
