\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Do you think you benefited from going to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 I did, I'm sure I did. I couldn't read like I do now my age if I didn't could I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 And you only regret that you couldn't have stayed longer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 I would like to have stayed on - liked to been - gone in for teacher I would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What would you have had to have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well see you got to study, go somewhere, a college sometimes haven't you and all like that to be a - qualified teacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 They used to have what they called pupil teachers in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes - well they used to 
- used to have extra lessons for that somewhere, I - rather - I forget now where we used to have it to. Well go to a night school I believe they did or something. They the one that go in for teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 While you were at school did you have any part time job to earn a little money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, I never used to do nothing. I used to mind me lessons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Except when you used to take the money for the blanket club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon? Yes, Saturday afternoon take the blanket club.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What was your first full time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh well see I went to over to the - over to the mine see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Which mine was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Tincroft.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh I - I don't know, I believe someone over there worked over there got it for me. You know, got the job f
or me. Somebody else working there, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What exactly did you have to do in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Packing at first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10973051\charrsid3556460 Packing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460  first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Great iron bar, not - hit the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10973051\charrsid3556460 keeves}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 , the tin and all, then I went in the tin yard first - after that, went in the tin yard and married from there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You would hit the keeves of tin?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Yes, keeves full of water and tin in it, and then you'd pack it with a iron bar, they had some packers, but they didn't pack hard enough for the l
ast time, and then we used to - pack it, and I used to do that between and - working around in the yard. Brush up the yard, sweep it up clean, you had to have the yard clean, my - my boots was so clean on the weekend nearly as they was at beginning. Unles
s it was rain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 That's the yard outside the main offices?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well they - they had a tin - proper tin dressers there, and when we finished with it they go in the tin house ready to be sent away. To be smelted. Men used to sack it up in sacks - weigh it out and sack it up and then it was sent away to the smelters.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 The tin would be in the state of sand at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You couldn't - you could - you had to be careful you didn't soil it. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How could you describe a keeve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What is a keeve like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Keeve, oh great round - like a great round tub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Is it a sort of a round table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well it was - more like a great round tub it was, and there was - water in it see, and then the men would - nul - two more would be here,
 and - one would be here and two would be stirring that, they stir that all up for wat - leave water run in it, and they would stir that up with a shovel, stirring that way. Do that way, and then when they stir it, this would all get thick, the work would
 be all in the water. And then that - that would - that'd be packed and that - that - water would all be packed out and - only the dry - work left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You would drain the water out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Very interest - very interesting it was. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 That was your first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, and then I stood in the same place only brush around - brush up the floor and - things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Do that all day long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What did you have to wear for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh we used to wear ordinary clothes and white aprons. 
And white handcuffs. Used to make handcuffs I did, wind them round your hands so far. Bring your thumb through that's all. That'll keep from getting the galls with the shovel, shovel held. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 That was to protect your hands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 When you're brushing up - yes, protection more that was for. Oh it was nice work. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You didn't have any uniform?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, nothing. Didn't want no uniforms see, just have your whit apron.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you wear anything on your head?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 After you finished packing the tin, what job did you go on to then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 After you finished doing the packing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Finished - packing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What job did you go on to then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well, go up in the - that was down on another floor, used to go up in the yard, and b
rush around and - used to attend the strip. Put the work - on the - floor, up in the strip with a shovel, small shovel for women, and then the water would wash that down, go into a bundle they call it. They wouldn}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10973051\charrsid3556460 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 t know what it was now, 'cos there isn't n
one of they going. They're all different now, it's no bundles nowhere now. Haven't for years. Then the men would clean that work off. And - and put it in the keeves. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How would you describe a strip?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Strip? Oh was - a thing - it was wood and m
ore of a boat shape see, only not so big, and then there was a line - a launder go across and the drippings of water, and that would wash the work down. Work down through like launderers they were on the bundles, and then that would go right around and th
e
y used to - the head - and - head and tail, the head was for go down to the keeve and the tail part - would be thrown on the floor and go through the - strip again. 'Til that was cleaned, and that would go down. Very interesting. Wasn't nothing you had to
 learn you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Would that be separating the tin from the sand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh yes. Wouldn't have no sand there in the tin floors. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Do you know how the work was organised, who told you what you had to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh well see we had - boss men there se
e. And the men to the keeves, the tin dressers, when you was packing, they would come and - and turn the hilt down and - see if it was hard, if it was hard enough you would stop. We was glad from that because the bar was hard - iron, yes. We used to be wa
iting for him to say that's hard enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How long would that generally take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
They got - had self packers see but they - they'd pack ordinary but not for the last time 'cos that had to be - hard you see, for that would be the tin then.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If it was packed hard it would take less room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Then they would clear - they would drain off all that water, the drop that was left, and - clear - take the wad out from the keeve and put it in a hand barrows, and two girls, one each end, would carry that into the tin house. And tip it in a pile.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Would take it in a barrel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Push it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well see they weren't a lot see, tin don't pile a lot in together, and these two girls would - be one each end of the - see, they would be barrels with no wheels, hand barrels, and they would carry the work in the tin house, very interesting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 They would be in shafts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You enjoyed the work did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh yes. I liked it. Very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Seven - seven in the morning 'til five for years. Then they altered it eight 'til five. But it used to be seven for years. I used to leave home half past six in the morning, when the foundry men - they used to work - go in half past six those days, and 
- leave work half past five, and I used to go when their - their whistle finished blowing I used to go. Long way to go it was see, took me all that time to get there at seven o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 About two miles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What were the roads like then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Oh not - I used to have go up over hills and - well you'd go through Dolcoath Mine more or less to get over to Tincraft, Dolcoath was first. Go through part of the Dolcoath Mine and go right on a big road and - get to Tincraft. Then Carn
 Brea station wasn't far from there. If it was pouring rain when I leave off, I used to go down to the station and - get in the train, 'cos my father used to be up that - station some days. And then it wasn't m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16214145\charrsid3556460 ore than two pence ride}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460  from there to Camborne station. That save a lot of wet wouldn't it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You used to ride home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 But not to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Just ride home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you work Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Saturdays used to go seven 'til one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Any Sunday work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well, we had - you - Whitson Monday morning, we used to have to do in six instead of seven, and leave off one. That would be our day's work then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 That would be Whit Monday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 That's a Whit Monday. Then you used to have Christmas Day you see, home. And - Good Friday for Easter, that's all I remember holiday.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Would you be paid for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, that. But if you stayed home the next day you would lose that day too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Can you remember what you were paid when you went to the mine first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 When I was married first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 When you went to the mine first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Oh - well - I had - four shilling a week first. Then I had five. And I - left - was married with five shilling a week, pound a month. All the women mostly had that, a pound a month. 'Cos the men didn't have much see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you think that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well that's all they was giving those days see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh I had to give all to mother, she was waiting for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What would it be spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh - for food and things see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How about your clothes then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 She used to get all that, mother did, yes. I never used to do nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How did you get on with the other people that you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Very nice. Very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Were there a lot of girls from Camborne?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well, no, not - was one or two - from down round here, but it wasn't in the tin yard, they was in the stamps floors. They done the rougher work, be
fore it get in to we. But it wasn't - no one in my - in where I worked not from Camborne, but me. There was Pool and Tuckingmill and - different places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How would you call it rougher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well you see, it was the work - brought there, before it - to
 be - tended to, and put through this here - keeves, this here strips until it was got nearly to the tin floors, then we had the best tin where I was to see work. That was the proper tin floors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Was it heavier work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, heavier stuff it was, dirty old work you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 All right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh all right, very nice he was. You mind your work you - nothing to worry about have you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Do you remember who your first employer was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Who what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Do you remember what your first employer's name was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He was called Williams from Tuckingmill, he was the big man. Will Williams he was called. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Was he the shift boss?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He was in the yard boss round us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did the job alter your attitude to school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did the job, once you started to work, did you feel the same attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well yes, I didn't used to take no notice of it you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You'd left school then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Used to have twenty minutes for - breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
About nine o'clock and come at twenty past nine. Go in - we had a - dinner house we used to call it, see, a woman in it to boil a kettle and - wash the cups you know she was kept there 
for that. And she would warm dinners for you if you had a pasty she'd warm it for dinnertime. Then you go twelve o'clock for that, and go back one. Go in and work one. Hour dinner. Very good that was. That's the only breaks we had, nothing in the afternoo
n.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Would you have preferred another type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well there wasn't - nothing - on those days see. Wasn't very many - unless they go in service you know and - not many of those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Were there any trades unions in those days?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Never heard tell of nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests, did they feel the same about conditions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, never used to dislike none of 'em, not - everything worked on right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you like full time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Full time? Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Do you think there was any difference between tradesmen and labourers in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well of course - there - tradesmen always got - more money than the labourers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Any other difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, not that I know - didn't - I didn't notice there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 It didn't affect their work in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you have to wear special sort of footwear for that work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Footwear? no, used to wear boots, lace up boots.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 I'd like to ask you about your life at home after you left school, you continued to live at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Would I - stay in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You still continued to live at home after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh - well - I did 'til I got work see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Starting work, did that make any difference to your home circumstances?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
It didn't change your relationship with your parents or your sisters in any way? You did say that your elder sister also worked in a mine, where did she work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 She worked with Streams, you mean Laura Jane? She worked in the Streams, down - Tol - Tolvaddon way down there somewhere.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Was that different to the work that you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Yes, she didn't have to do what I did, I don't know what she used to do but she used to work Streams, it wasn't a tin mine see. It was the Streams, they clean what come from the - mines all rundown that way if you understand me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 They clean what's left over?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well used - their lea}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16214145\charrsid3556460 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 t run down there way - the waste used to go down that way you see. But over her place was the proper tin place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did she have to handle the big heavy things for packing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Not the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You were saying about you would protect your hands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh that was only, you see when you was using the shovel, the hilt might - go over your fi
ngers a bit, I've got a few galls there but - that's what we used to protect our hands - from.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If you had a serious -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Some never used - lots never used to wear none but I was in the choir, I wanted to keep me hands bit - decent didn't I, but lot
 of - lot of girls didn't used to wear no handcuffs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What would happen then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well they would just use the shovel with their hands see. They were older some of them and I suppose the skin was tight or something.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If you got a serious cut would they be able to treat it there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If you got a serious cut on your hand would they be able to treat it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh yes, we never used to get no - nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you continue after you started to work, you continued to go to Sunday school just as before?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Went Sunday school and the choir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you go in for more singing at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Go in for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You were saying about your interest in singing, did that increase as you got older, after you went to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh I went - still go there in the choir and go round - I used to go different places to sing you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Different chapels?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Me and Miss Miller used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you have any training, voice training?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, I never had no training. 
Had - only from the choir you know, that organist. Never had no special training. We had to pay smart for that. You had to pay a lot of money for be trained.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 But the choirmaster would do something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well he would - train us there for his work in 
the choir and - I used to - if I hear anyone else sing a song, I would try get that and I would sing it myself, I'd learn it, see, and he'd play it and - I'd do it. I could pick it up very well. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Who taught you to play the organ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well there's
 - a - a neighbour we had there in our row, he - used to - learn me to play - the organ. Come down my house he did and learnt me to play, used to live up top of our row. And that's that's as I learnt. But he never used to charge mother very much. No.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Where did father buy the organ then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Father bought the organ locally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Yes. Lovely organ it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you take any interest in politics?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, I never used to take no interest in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you go out of an evening after you started to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
In the evenings, oh in and out, not very much. Used to go to choir practice. Tuesday nights. And - might go out - a night after in the week, not very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Who with normally, who would you go out with normally of an evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Who I'd go out with? Oh I never used to go out with no - go out nowhere, not - walking, not till I went courting. I used to just go choir practice, that's all. I didn't used to run the streets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Was Mr Tresidder in your choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Your husband, was he in your choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, in the - we was married from - two of us from the same choir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 So that's where you met him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He wouldn't be one of any new friends that you made through work? You would have met him before you went to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well - oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you make any new friends, boys or girls, from going to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well you see then when - he used to work over the same place see, first, before the mine - closed, then we went Crofty, but he worke
d Tincroft too, and when he was dark mornings he used to come up my place and put me over. 'Cos I was afraid when it was dark mornings. 'Cos it was a lonely road. Mm. Well in the dark mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you have a lantern?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No street lamps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No. Well - not - not - to - across where the mine was, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Were you able to bring friends home of an evening or did you want to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Bring friends home of an evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well no, we never used 'cos we was - enough ourselves weren't we to entertain, family and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did mother and father expect you to be home at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well yes, I never used to be late in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You had to be up very early?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did they expect to know where you were if you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well of course they knew when I went practice where}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16214145\charrsid3556460 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 s was but that was nearby. And - after it was over I'd come in you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 I think you said you were almost twenty-one when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Just twenty-one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You'd know your husband then since a child had you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh we were - going together for years you know, I was going to say like children met but not very old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You met at chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. I used to go down his place nearly every Sunday dinner from chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He came from Camborne as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Wheal Gerry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you save up money before getting married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well I couldn't save very much but - I used to - buy a bit of - few things in and out and made all me own pillowcases and - croch - trimming to go to t
hem and - things like that or - we'd go out anywhere, a town, and we see anything and it wasn't very expensive, well we'd buy that and put it aside and saved up quite a few for the home - things. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What they used to call the bottom drawer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, that's right, bottom drawer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did your parents help in setting up your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Were you engaged very long, or did people get engaged in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well yes, I was engaged - quite - well - little while before marriage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Could you describe your wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh we -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Where were you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Married Centenary Chapel where I went to - the choir, some came. And the - organ - organist was there, and I had hymns and - there - there was a minister called the Reverend Slack
, he was here that time, tall man, and he used to go Wes - belong Wesley and Centenary, lived up Beacon Hill, well he married us, and then there were landaus, those days, not cars. And we went out for a drive after the wedding, and then come back and had 
our lunch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Married in the morning were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Married eleven o'clock. Then we went out for a ride and come back and had our lunch, bit later than ordinary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Just you and your husband went for the drive?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well no, the two - my two sisters w
ent, and me - and - my husband's brother's young lady, they were married after we, they - she went. And this uncle - he got the taxi for us to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 This was the landau?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, landau. All opened out. That's what they used to do those days, go for a drive after. Landua drive they used to call it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Where did you go, do you remember?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh I couldn't tell you, all around out around the country places see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Then you came back to your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Lunch and then - yes, then we stayed there 
then and - had - the other part of the family, visitors come you know. Had the reception at mother's home of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 And the guests would be members of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you have present sin those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh yes, I had quite a lot of presents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did people have a honeymoon then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well some did but not many. They're mostly - you know, people that were a bit better off would go off and - they used to wear white, lots did. But - ordinary people, I didn't have that, I had }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16214145\charrsid3556460 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 e blue
. Pale blue dress and black chiffon hat we used to wear those days, with a black feather in it, and a white one. Oh I was looking rather nice, white kid gloves, and they used to have a yoke in the dress then, front and back, white silk, and a big white sa
sh tied behind. Oh was looking quite nice. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Who made your dress?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well she was called - Beattie Buzza, used to belong in the choir with me, she made it. Mm. She was a dressmaker you see, and she came to my mother's place and made it. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did they have bridesmaids and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well my two sisters went see there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did they have special dresses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well they had - they had skirts and blouses, that was most the go then, navy skirt and biscuit coloured silk blouses. They wore.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did they carry bouquets then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, a spray of flowers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Where did you live after you were married?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 In the same row, only - number twenty instead of twelve where I - lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How long did you stay at number twenty then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How long did you live there at number twenty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh - quite a little while. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 And then you went to live with your mother-in-law?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 My husband's people, down to Wheal Gerry, I one - I was down there six years. Then I went back in th
e old row again. And there I stood 'til me husband was buried.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How old was your husband when you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He was - he's two year and three months older than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 So he was about twenty-three?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 And his job at the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 His job at the time when you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh the same as - he always did the same work, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Never ever had any other job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, he never - my people was never nothing for moving about jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did he do any casual or part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Who?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did your husband do any casual or part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Oh well he was handy with a - trowel, he - put in - he'd put in fireplaces for people and - he helped put in stoves. Part time you know for - overtime work we call.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He'd do a bit of masonry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, 'cos we was glad to get - money then, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He was very involved with the band wasn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Was your husband in the band at the time you were married? Was he in the Camborne town band?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, before I was married. He was there fifty-three years, a drummer. He had a lovely fireside chair presented to him - for his services.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 When you married you didn't continue to work then did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Me, no, I - I never worked after I - yes, I left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You never went out to work again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How did your husband like his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Oh never hear him complain. He couldn't have 'cos he was - late before - he was in his seventies before he retired. Then he was brought home sick, that's how. So he must have liked his job mustn't he? Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 They could work on then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You had six children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You had six children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Like as children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How many children did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh I - had - five. One died, I've got four living now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Were they all born at home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, all home, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 In those days in childbirth how did you manage, did you have someone to come and look after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Someone look after me? Well my mother done it sometime, and - once one of the ne
ighbours did it. They were very good those days the - neighbours used to - help out each other that way you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You didn't have a professional nurse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, I had a nurse when I had the baby.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you have the doctor as well or just the nurse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 I had the doctor twice. First baby and the second.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You knew what to expect in childbirth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well, my - my husband's mother you see, used to - go with people when they had their babies, and then we used to have - have the doctor then, but w
hen you had a special nurse you didn't want the doctor unless it was necessary. So I didn't have the doctor on the others. Just the nurse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Your mother had had several babies after you were quite a big girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 So you knew exactly what to expect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How long did you have to stay in bed then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Ten days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How did your husband manage when you were laid up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh well he would do what he could too you see, he always - took to do - domestic work if it was needed, help. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What did the nurse do for the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh wash and dress the baby always. And wash me and tend to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Just for the ten days?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Ten days, then she finished then. You get up then you see. But never used to go out, I wasn't allow
ed to go out 'til the end of the month. Mother wouldn't let me go out, 'til - it isn't like they are today, out in the - whatnot, she wouldn't allow me to. They was afraid you'd take cold see. People were more particular those days than they are today.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If anything went wrong in those days it would be bad wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you feed your baby yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Bottle fed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Had bottle fed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Was there any special reason for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well I couldn't - I never had no nipples see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You weren't able to breast feed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. No, I wasn't able to do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If you needed any advice about the baby who would you ask?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If you needed any advice about the baby or yourself, who would you ask?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh well I would ask me mother or one of the older neighbours beside of me. They were all very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 In those days if baby was asleep would you wake it up to feed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, leave it sleep on. I had so much work to do, I was for glad for him to sleep.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If he cried before the normal time would you take him up and feed him or let him cry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well - well yes, I have done so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If he didn't seem hungry would you be worried or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 When did the baby first take solid food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 They was very good - in that - eating their food, my children was, I never had no trouble. Yes, very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 When did they start having solid food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 When did they start having solid food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh not - very early, I didn't believe in giving t
hem solid food too early, I might give them bit of mashed potato or things like that but not no - heavy - pastry or nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He would be weaned from the milk at about six months old would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh well you see, if they would go off the bottle them
selves when they didn't want it you see, and then you'd give 'em a drink see with a cup or - something you see. But we would keep it on as long as they would take it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did your husband have much to do with bringing on the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Bring on the children, oh yes, he had to help.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did he ever feed them or change them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, he've done it night time. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He would do anything for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Let you rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. He would do anything for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Get them to sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Would he get them to sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What about attending to them in the night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What about attending to them in the night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well you see I - if they wanted any milk or anything in the night he would get out we
 had a methyated lamp, and he would warm the milk while I changed the baby. And the we'd go - feed it and go off again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Would he take them out sometimes without you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Yes. Always took to the children, and after they grown up he was always with his children. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If you were away singing did he take care of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He used to have them then. And my mother used to look in you know, but he - looked after them, while I was away singing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Then Sunday you were in the choir, he would help with food and that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh yes. Do any - work that was to be done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you think it did the baby any harm to cry? Some people used to think it did them harm to cry, what did you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well no, I didn't used to leave him cry too much, I
 didn't believe in that. Some used to say leave him to cry, when they're tired they'll stop, I didn't like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How did you manage the housekeeping in those early years? When you set up married life first, you managed with the housekeeping all right?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, but I - we had - we was all like that. Coming on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Some people say they never knew that their husband earned, was that the case with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No, my husband never opened his pay packet. All the years we were married. Nor my sons never do 
their wives. Bring home their pay packet as they have it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you talk it over how it was to be spent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you and your husband talk it over, about how it was to be spent?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well he used know that 'cos he used go do a lot of the shopping for me. 'Cos I couldn't always go when the family see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You would plan it together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, everything. He knew all what we spent and I knew what he spent, 'cos we never had nothing to waste.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 How many rooms were there in your house at Centenary Row?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Three. Three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Just like your mother's house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Same size.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Any relatives or lodgers living with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Nobody - no, only me and he.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 There was no question of paid help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 The washing, was that done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Was the washing done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Yes, we had a little wash house out in the garden. I used to do me own washing, and I like that. Nobody couldn't do my washing if I was able. Love it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you have a fire in the wash house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, a little fringle. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 That would be lit on Mondays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, and he used to - light it before he'd go work for me. Then while I was doing the other things, the water would be hot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Ready for the clothes to be put in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Were the family clothes made or mended by you or your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Done -?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did you make the family's clothes, you or your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 I have made some, but not - all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Were they always new or sometimes second hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well I - as I could get them you know, if I could get anything second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16214145\charrsid3556460  }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 hand I would, a suit, and - but their Sunday clothes used to be new from the shops generally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 If you had anything second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16214145\charrsid3556460  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 hand would it be bought from friends or were there any second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16214145\charrsid3556460  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 hand shops in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well, sometimes you could - buy them off friends see if they had them - gone too small for theirs, you might have them see. Sometimes they used to be a gift, and sometimes you would give something for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What about shoes, boots?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh I'd buy those, I'd buy those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 You didn't ever have them made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 They would be new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 They would be new, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did your husband help with cooking or washing in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Help with the cooking? Oh yes, he would do what he could towards it, peel vegetables and - he could fry and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Clearing up, would he do anything about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Fires, he would light this wash house fire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He would light the - fire, the days that he was home you know any time, he would light it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Any decorating, did he do any decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He would do a lot of it, but couldn't use papery, but he would do painting and - well mason and anything wanted do like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Was this home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Rent. Oh yes. Used to pay rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Who was your landlord there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 
Well the house I went in when I was married was - she was called Mr Thomas, you know, Mrs - not know a lot Centenary Row do ee? She - well her granny, she - Mrs Thomas they live
d down - Moor Street. Used to belong to her, a very - she never had no husband, woman - widow, and she was very nice. Used to pay nine and tuppence a month. That's nice rent wasn't it? That was - that was enough those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Quite a share of your wages really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did your husband help with the children, such as dressing or undressing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh yes, he would put them to bed - very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Bathing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did he ever read aloud to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Read aloud to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well - not very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Tell them stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, for them go bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did he ever take them out without you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. Yes, he'd put them down town and look around a bit or - if I wasn't able to go when the tea treat was he would go wit
h them. But he was in the band for years and years see, all the time we had children.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What time did the children go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Children? Oh they didn't used to be late because they had to get up for school you see. Eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did the children have any jobs to do to help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well no, they never used to do very much. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 When they got older did they help the little ones, the bigger ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh yes. They used to - big ones used to help dress the little ones and - put them out, you know, with 'em. Very good for that they were.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What room did you use for bathing them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What room was used to bath them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What rooms? With the bath in? Oh I bathed them down in the kitchen beside the fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 The big main living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, very good size.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 That would be Friday nights?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did the children all share the one big bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Meals were eaten in the big main kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 In the kitchen, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 And the cooking range was there as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What time was breakfast eaten at your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What time was breakfast eaten in your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well see we used to have breakfast after they come down and wash, and then have breakfast and then get their coats on and go school see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 And your husband, he'd have his before that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 He'd have his and go work, he would get out in the mornings early and go work see. I used to have to get them out in the morning go school.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Did he work shifts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Yes. But he used work always by day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What were his hours then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 What hours did he work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Oh he used to go - eight 'til five, and - then you see the children were all home for tea before then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Would he have a main meal when he came home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Have his meal, yes. We used to wait and have our tea all together.
