Well they used to - people I used to think of course I know people are good to their children now, but - he was nothing - doing like there is these
 days, they were more home in with their children wasn't they. Wasn't nothing to - you could go to more than just chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Would they kiss their children goodnight and that sort of thing? Did they show affection in that way?
