Well - I can only remember - my mother's step-mother. See my mother's - mother's mother died when she was about seven. And then - years went on and her father got married again, I can never remember him, I didn't know nothing about -
 her father, and then - she had a step-mother. She was called granny Nancarrow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 They lived in Redruth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2064242 MT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 Well she - no, they was out here then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15611786 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6842155\charrsid3556460 They came from Redruth?
